Localization.Name: UNE Unification War Medal (Damaged)
Localization.Description: A campaign medal from the United Nations of Earth (UNE) military that commemorates meritorious service during the Unification Wars (2380-2384). Considered to be in poor condition due to the faded ribbons colors and broken, corroded metal.
